\c 53
\s Vanhu vese vakashata
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. NeMaharati. Masikiri, \add Pisarema\add* raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumoyo maro: Hakuna Mwari. Vakaora, vakaita uipi hunonyangadza; hakuna anoita zvakanaka.
\v 2 Mwari wakatarisa pasi ari kumatenga pamusoro pevanakomana vevanhu, kuona kana pane anonzwisisa, anotsvaka Mwari.
\v 3 Umwe neumwe wavo wakadzokera shure, vakasvibiswa vese; hakuna anoita zvakanaka, hakuna neumwe.
\v 4 Vaiti vezvakaipa havana zivo here? Avo vanodya vanhu vangu \add se\add*vanodya chingwa, havadani kuna Mwari.
\v 5 Ipapo vaitya zvekutya, pasina chinotyisa, nokuti Mwari wakaparadzira mapfupa eanokudzikirai musasa, makavanyadzisa, nokuti Mwari wakavazvidza.
\p
\v 6 Dai ruponeso rwaIsraeri rwaibva paZiyoni! Mwari paanodzosa utapwa hwevanhu vake, Jakove achafara, Israeri achapembera.
